86
00:04:50,410 --> 00:04:54,440
So the travel ban targeted the country that
had the outbreak,

87
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:57,180
not Chinese people.

88
00:04:57,180 --> 00:05:00,120
So really, when it comes to media and governments,

89
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,930
what we’ve been seeing is not racism,

90
00:05:02,930 --> 00:05:08,220
but words and actions specifically targeted
at the country of China

91
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:13,440
and its ruling regime, the Chinese Communist
Party.

92
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:18,150
But that nuance is intentionally ignored by
the Chinese Communist Party

93
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:20,490
