Party’s narrative

171
00:09:42,579 --> 00:09:44,600
about racism.

172
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:49,260
For example, after a US congressman referred
to the “Wuhan virus” in a tweet...

173
00:09:49,260 --> 00:09:54,529
