stirred a ‘racism’ debate.

174
00:09:54,529 --> 00:10:00,339
“GOP lawmakers continue to use ‘Wuhan
virus’ or ‘Chinese coronavirus’”.

175
00:10:00,339 --> 00:10:03,860
