is just a bonus.

192
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:03,610
So dear viewers, I have a suggestion.

193
00:11:03,610 --> 00:11:09,740
Let’s not call it the “Wuhan coronavirus”
or the “Chinese coronavirus.”

194
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:13,990
It was the Chinese Communist Party that turned
a small number of infections

195
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:16,689
into a global pandemic by covering it up—

196
00:11:16,689 --> 00:11:20,730
and that’s exactly what they’re trying
to distract us from.

197
00:11:20,730 --> 00:11:26,449
So let’s call it what it really is: The
“CCP Coronavirus.”

